{"tid":1514933,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嘈到12點好停，炒車件事當上咗一堂，繼續對準政權，不分化","createTime":"2019-08-29T02:57:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T05:08:18.000Z","uid":76674,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8cab8d8bf09147715f5729fc5fa814a04a6f6f8e","tid":1514933,"uid":76674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:57:20.000Z","msg":"成版幾個post屌嚟屌去有咩用<br />\n補救到咩？出完氣件事一樣發生咗<br />\n雖然不完美，甚至好錯，但我都唔會割蓆<br />\n大家當上咗一堂課，吸取經驗<br />\n當日吹話要fake news嗰班都已經笠哂水<br />\n亦唔排除有黑警上嚟繼續互屌，挑起矛盾分化<br />\n件事就由佢冷處理，我亦相信香港人既智慧，唔會同一件事衰2次<br />\n更唔想5年前因內部分化令我地既抗爭被瓦解<br />\n不割蓆，不分化<br />\n呢個係5年前既失敗學返嚟既<br />\n大家可以繼續討論件事<br />\n但傾到中午12點好啦，全部人同我推返831post<br />\n對準政權<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可"},{"pid":"d5999330c9720b33b7fd4103bc81ac8a14fc2c17","tid":1514933,"uid":35842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:57:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OTykUks.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOTykUks.jpg&h=e262c427&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3J6Zqr9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3J6Zqr9.jpg&h=398279dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wjFi3Tp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwjFi3Tp.jpg&h=1a5d1359&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">901 和你塞 13:00 見</span></span> <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTKb0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=8c79962e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\n現有文宣集合 (Google Drive)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTKb0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk